# Бой

**FSM:** choice → ready → countdown → play ⇄ **emergency** → explosion → ready|result. First card at countdown end if null. After boom: next_card→next_player→ready.

**UI init trap:** FSM starts in `initialize()` before child `_ready`. HUD + `game_input` MUST `_sync_to_current_state()` in `_ready`.

**Layout:** `BackgroundBomb` + `MenuBombLayout`/`GameBombBackground` (`Background.png`, cover 1080×1920). Battle UI in `ScaledContent` design coords. Markers: `PlayerName` (name plate + lighten overlay), `RoundWord` (syllable/countdown on dial). No round bomb sprite.

**HUD** (`game_hud.gd`, accent `#F5470A`): PlayerStrip@`PlayerName` · SyllableCard@`RoundWord` · ActionHints(y~1120) · countdown@`RoundWord` · explosion overlay · ResultPanel (screen). No edge vignette.

State UI: choice=«Выбираем первого»+pulse · ready=«Первым ходит»+StartRoundButton · play=full HUD · explosion=name overlay.

**Input** (`game_input.gd`): `mouse_filter=IGNORE`. PLAY: multi-touch pass — next only when **all** fingers up within **0.3s**; hold longer = invalid · tap→next + sparks. **Emergency** button (PLAY only) → `EMERGENCY` state, pause game+audio, overlay to re-pick current player · continue → `try_add_bonus_bomb_time()`. RESULT→menu.

**Pass sparks:** `pass_bomb_spark_layer.gd` on `ScaledContent` — radial additive fire burst at touch (one-shot CPUParticles2D).

**Emergency:** `BattleEmergencyOverlay` + `EmergencyState` · `PlayerSelectionWidget.set_emergency_mode()` · `GameBattleChrome/EmergencyButton` · icon `icon_emergency.svg`.

**Battle lobby overlay:** `BattlePlayerLobbyOverlay` — edit roster mid-game · Done = confirm if roster ok else click · reuses `PlayerSelectionWidget` + `StartActionButton`.

**Visual:** `GameBombBackground` — player-color backdrop via `SlimeColors`, alert pulse, bomb flash/shake on explosion · particles at (540,1050).

**Audio:** gameplay → `GameSound` · UI buttons → `UiSounds` → `audio.mdc`.

**Core:** `game_manager.gd` `game_session.gd` `game_sound.gd` `word_condition.gd`
